Author: GigiHowell
Text: I understand what you're going through...and it's tough..I've found that reading weight loss books, and watching vids or listening to podcast seems to help me..here is one of those ebooks...[https://lnkmeup.com/6wnu](https://lnkmeup.com/6wnu) . Keeping busy doing things helps me a lot!! Try focusing on these kinds of things when you get the binge feeling!!
